WEBVTT

00:00:59.120 --> 00:01:01.776
Jarrett looked to the instrument
a little warily,

00:01:01.800 --> 00:01:03.336
played a few notes,

00:01:03.360 --> 00:01:04.575
walked around it,

00:01:04.599 --> 00:01:06.056
played a few more notes,

00:01:06.080 --> 00:01:07.776
muttered something to his producer.

00:01:07.800 --> 00:01:11.120
Then the producer
came over to Vera and said ...

00:01:12.280 --> 00:01:15.840
"If you don't get a new piano,
Keith can't play."

00:01:18.000 --> 00:01:19.456
There'd been a mistake.

00:01:19.480 --> 00:01:21.856
The opera house had provided
the wrong instrument.

00:01:21.880 --> 00:01:24.536
This one had this harsh,
tinny upper register,

00:01:24.560 --> 00:01:26.840
because all the felt had worn away.

00:01:27.640 --> 00:01:30.776
The black notes were sticking,